==Shange Tang 

~~~
{}{img_left}{bio.jpg}{}{140}{203}{}
I am a researcher at OpenAI.
I obtained my Ph.D. degree at Princeton University in 2026, advised by Professor [https://fan.princeton.edu/ Jianqing Fan] and Professor [https://sites.google.com/view/cjin/home Chi Jin]. I received my bachelor's degree from School of Mathematical Sciences at Peking University in 2021.\n
I am interested in theory and applications of statistics and machine learning.\n
E-mail: /shangetang/ \[@\] princeton \[DOT\] edu \n
[https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=UmITOE0AAAAJ Google Scholar] \n
[https://www.linkedin.com/in/shange-tang-8875b5207/ LinkedIn]
